rows.label: soul23_P0101
rows.name: I'm attacking! Move in!

rows.label: soul23_P0102
rows.name:
I'll take the lead.
 Close in and stagger them!

rows.label: soul23_P0103
rows.name:
Close the distance and
 take control!

rows.label: soul23_P0201
rows.name:
I'll start things at range.
 Follow my lead!

rows.label: soul23_P0202
rows.name:
I'll keep them in check.
 You buff us up!

rows.label: soul23_P0203
rows.name: With me! Cripple them!

rows.label: soul23_P0301
rows.name: Take the initiative! Close in!

rows.label: soul23_P0302
rows.name: Lay down suppressing fire!

rows.label: soul23_P0303
rows.name: Get your auras ready!

rows.label: soul23_P0401
rows.name:
They're gaining ground!
 I need recovery!

rows.label: soul23_P0402
rows.name:
This is starting to take its toll.
 I need assistance!

rows.label: soul23_P0403
rows.name: I can handle this... Buff me up!

rows.label: soul23_P0501
rows.name: I have to hold out... Heal me!

rows.label: soul23_P0502
rows.name: Recovery, please! I'm in trouble!

rows.label: soul23_P0503
rows.name:
I will not retreat! Buff me up
 and I'll push them back!

rows.label: soul23_P0601
rows.name:
Move in now...
 while you still can...

rows.label: soul23_P0602
rows.name:
Leave me! Just unload on
 them with all...you've got...

rows.label: soul23_P0603
rows.name:
Use an aura... You can
 still change this...

rows.label: soul23_P0701
rows.name: Success! Now move in!

rows.label: soul23_P0702
rows.name: Yes! Attack at range!

rows.label: soul23_P0703
rows.name:
Weaken them and put them
 on the defensive!

rows.label: soul23_P0801
rows.name:
Hope they didn't need that.
 Now use melee attacks!

rows.label: soul23_P0802
rows.name:
Now's your chance! Fire on
 them to topple them!

rows.label: soul23_P0803
rows.name:
That should cramp their style.
 Cripple them!

rows.label: soul23_P0901
rows.name:
They're shaken.
 Fire on them now!

rows.label: soul23_P0902
rows.name:
We need to buff up if we're going
 to handle an adversary this large.

rows.label: soul23_P0903
rows.name:
It's all over if we let them
 overwhelm us! Use Overclock!

rows.label: soul23_P1001
rows.name: That's it. Melee strikes!

rows.label: soul23_P1002
rows.name: Cover fire! I see an opening!

rows.label: soul23_P1003
rows.name:
Cripple them now and we'll
 be in good shape!

rows.label: soul23_P1101
rows.name:
Use an aura to heighten your
 power, then don't let up!

rows.label: soul23_P1102
rows.name: Prepare now. Auras up!

rows.label: soul23_P1103
rows.name:
Buff up and get back on the
 offensive!

rows.label: soul23_P1201
rows.name:
Overclock! Dial it all
 the way up!

rows.label: soul23_P1202
rows.name:
Follow me! I'll push them back
 with Overclock!

rows.label: soul23_P1203
rows.name:
I'll take the lead! Put up an
 aura and stay with me!

rows.label: soul23_C0101
rows.name: There are still more! Move in!

rows.label: soul23_C0102
rows.name:
Stay sharp! Seek out a
 new target and fire!

rows.label: soul23_C0103
rows.name: Buff up now!

rows.label: soul23_C0201
rows.name: Predictable! Use an aura!

rows.label: soul23_C0202
rows.name: I'll draw them away. Buff up!

rows.label: soul23_C0203
rows.name:
Check out this footwork!
 Attack at range!

rows.label: soul23_C0301
rows.name:
There! Now get in another
 melee strike!

rows.label: soul23_C0302
rows.name:
Attack at range for
 good measure!

rows.label: soul23_C0303
rows.name:
There we go!
 Now get in their face!

rows.label: soul23_C0401
rows.name:
The weather's against us.
 Brace!

rows.label: soul23_C0402
rows.name:
The weather's changing.
 Use an aura and hold out!

rows.label: soul23_C0403
rows.name:
Let us turn this weather into a
 weapon. Weaken the enemy!

rows.label: soul23_C0501
rows.name:
I'll confuse them! Look for an
 opportunity to buff up!

rows.label: soul23_C0502
rows.name:
I'll draw their attention!
 Buff up and regroup!

rows.label: soul23_C0503
rows.name:
Use Overclock!
 I'll swing around!

rows.label: soul23_C0601
rows.name: Don't worry. I'll be all right.

rows.label: soul23_C0602
rows.name:
That's better, thanks. Now give
 me some suppressive fire!

rows.label: soul23_C0603
rows.name:
You have my thanks.
 Now buff up!

rows.label: soul23_C0701
rows.name:
Thank you.
 We need to fortify!

rows.label: soul23_C0702
rows.name:
I owe you. Let's buff up and
 tear them a new one!

rows.label: soul23_C0703
rows.name:
I'm fine, but you
 need an aura!

rows.label: soul23_C0801
rows.name: No whining! We're going in!

rows.label: soul23_C0802
rows.name:
I'm busting through!
 Cover fire!

rows.label: soul23_C0803
rows.name: I refuse to run! Buff me up!

rows.label: soul23_C0901
rows.name:
Up here! Now shoot them
 while they're distracted!

rows.label: soul23_C0902
rows.name:
Attack from all angles!
 Ready? Fire!

rows.label: soul23_C0903
rows.name:
I've got a clear view from here.
 Get ready to take the shot!

rows.label: soul23_C1001
rows.name:
It's down! Move in and
 take a swing!

rows.label: soul23_C1002
rows.name:
Now! Aim for the
 toppled enemy!

rows.label: soul23_C1003
rows.name: Weaken it before it gets up!

rows.label: soul23_C1101
rows.name: I stopped it cold! Close in!

rows.label: soul23_C1102
rows.name: It's dizzy! Shoot it now!

rows.label: soul23_C1103
rows.name:
Cripple it now while
 it can't move!

rows.label: soul23_C1201
rows.name:
Uh-oh. Someone needs a little
 wake-up kiss!

rows.label: soul23_C1202
rows.name:
Don't fall asleep, now.
 Someone might shoot you!

rows.label: soul23_C1203
rows.name:
A little fire ought to wake this
 sleeping beauty up!

rows.label: soul23_C1301
rows.name: I'll hold it! Attack up close!

rows.label: soul23_C1302
rows.name: I've got 'em pinned! Fire now!

rows.label: soul23_C1303
rows.name: I'll try and hold it! Move in!

rows.label: soul23_C1401
rows.name:
This is nothing as long as
 I get it fixed early!

rows.label: soul23_C1402
rows.name:
Forget about me!
 Just strike back!

rows.label: soul23_C1403
rows.name: Where was I hit? Cover fire!

rows.label: soul23_C1501
rows.name:
No! My Doll! We need to
 heal and regroup!

rows.label: soul23_C1502
rows.name:
Ugh, that's not good...
 Buff up, please!

rows.label: soul23_C1503
rows.name:
We can't afford to lose any
 momentum. Use Overclock!

rows.label: soul23_C1601
rows.name:
I've got a fuel problem!
 Gimme a fix!

rows.label: soul23_C1602
rows.name: Low fuel! I need a re-up!

rows.label: soul23_C1603
rows.name:
I'm burning right through
 my fuel. Help me out!
